net.sourceforge.fastupload

Class MultiPartDiskFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.fastupload.MultiPart
      • net.sourceforge.fastupload.MultiPartDiskFile
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MultiPartBinaryFile, MultiPartTextFile

    public abstract class MultiPartDiskFile
extends MultiPart
    A abstract sub class of MultiPart. The class provides write data of multipart/form-data boundary into a disk file. just convert file name with specified charset
    Author:
    Link Qian
